OL,3,CNew Guernsey legislation for 'no-
OL,4,Cfault' divorces is delayed
OL,6,FNew laws to allow 'no-fault' divorces
OL,7,Fin have been delayed.
OL,9,FThe Matrimonial Causes Law will allow
OL,10,Fcouples to separate without having to
OL,11,Fprovide a reason.
OL,13,FThe approved the law in July 2022 and
OL,14,Fwas expected to be introduced at the
OL,15,Fend of 2023, but has now been
OL,16,Fpostponed.
OL,18,FThe States said: "The implementation
OL,19,Fprocess is taking longer than expected
OL,20,Fdue to the prioritisation of more
OL,21,Furgent legislation."
