OL,3,CNew Guernsey legislation for 'no-
OL,4,Cfault' divorces is delayed
OL,6,FThe change would bring Guernsey laws
OL,7,Fin line with England and Wales, which
OL,8,Fintroduced 'no-fault' divorces in 2022.
OL,10,FThe process is not yet in place in
OL,11,FJersey.
OL,13,FGuernsey's new legislation will also
OL,14,Fremove the ability to contest a
OL,15,Fdivorce and remove the requirement for
OL,16,Fthe court to consider reconciliation.
OL,18,FThe reforms are now expected for the
OL,19,Fend of June 2024.
